# Contributing to <%Name%>

## Prerequisites

- **PowerShell 7.2+**
- [Anvil](https://github.com/f0oster/Anvil) (`Install-Module -Name Anvil -Scope CurrentUser`)

## Setup

```powershell
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <%Name%>
Invoke-AnvilBootstrapDeps
```

## Development

```powershell
Invoke-AnvilBuild -Task Lint, Test
```

Run the full pipeline before submitting:

```powershell
Invoke-AnvilBuild
```

To test your changes interactively:

```powershell
Import-AnvilModule
```

## Conventions

- One function per file, filename matches function name
- Public functions in `src/<%Name%>/Public/`, private in `Private/`

## Testing

Unit tests cover individual functions. Integration tests validate the compiled build output. Both must pass before merging.

When adding a new private function, include an "is not exported" test in the test file.

## Pull requests

1. Branch from `main`
2. Run `Invoke-AnvilBuild` and ensure it passes
3. Open a PR against `main`
